N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 613.10 - Complaints

State Regulations

The oversight committee may receive
and investigate complaints against organizations providing representation to
indigent defendants and the attorneys in their employ which relate to the
discharge of an organization's or an individual attorney's duties pursuant to
an order of appointment, and shall, subject to the approval of the Appellate

Division, adopt rules for the processing of such complaints. Notes
